{"tid":1710321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【好行夾唔送】李力持請同胞勿到港讀書 網民召喚：李導回大陸生活","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:21:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c1a12e0f4e96e189d6a2e073b0f49efb708196","tid":1710321,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"逆權運動未成功，昨日殤11，魔警在西灣河開槍射中青年，交通警騎鐵馬瘋撞市民，民怨沸騰，抗爭運動至今已逾2000人被捕，其中不少是大學生！上月底理工大學舉行畢業禮，有部份畢業生在校園發起蒙面快閃行動，戴「V煞」面具抗議校長滕錦光自我審查，拒絕與戴口罩畢業生握手。<br />\n昨晚導演李力持在微博貼高登討論區的理大畢業相，寄語他的大陸同胞：「懇請各位內地同胞，千萬不要送仔女去香港讀大學！現在在讀的學生也可能認真考慮退學，生命受嚴重威脅，一定要小心。」跟李力持同聲同氣的大陸網民當然拍手叫好，更有網民苦口婆心勸李力持：「李導回大陸來生活吧，看着地獄般的hk，實在窩心。」不知李力持會否聽從民意，搬到大灣區居住呢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191112/large/1573535991_a345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191112%2Flarge%2F1573535991_a345.jpg&h=3c2c3f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191112/60257571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257571&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEcowRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=35f9e01f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257571&h=1aaf8d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191112/60257571</a>"},{"pid":"787ca56b9badf414dd2512573d7ab3b164e80851","tid":1710321,"uid":3962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33daf8fbcb95b6f3ba35f2be48d32da7029b7d97","tid":1710321,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"每日個150個心諗<br />\n你都痴撚線"},{"pid":"c57ac29233233e7af0178fb346cf9030